### 4. Cooldown auto-refresh loop runs forever on a `LaunchedEffect`
```kotlin
LaunchedEffect(socialTasksResource) {
    val hasAnyCooldown = tasks.any { it.nextAvailableAt != null }
    if (hasAnyCooldown) {
