When `socialTasksResource` changes (which it will after `loadUserSocialTasks` returns), this `LaunchedEffect` restarts, creating **a new infinite loop on top of any existing one**. Use a `rememberCoroutineScope` + manual job management or a separate flag to prevent duplicate loops.

